Maintainer: Cecilia Campanile <cecilia.campanile@ndorms.ox.ac.uk>
Description: Provides tools to validate and explore 'summarised_result' objects
    produced when working with the Observational Medical Outcomes Partnership
    (OMOP) Common Data Model. Checks that results are correctly formatted and 
    adequately suppressed, and provides utilities to explore and understand 
    their content.
